                        </choice> Erythronium</add>, Lilium, Fritillaria, Tulipa, Gagea, <lb/>
                    <del rendition="#s">f</del> Yucca) fehlen meines Wissens am <lb/>
                    <placeName key="H0000355">Cap</placeName> gänzlich<supplied cert="high">.</supplied>
                </p>
                <p>
